OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright and occasional sunny
OL,6,Fspells with some showers developing,
OL,7,Fthese will be light for most places
OL,8,Fbut a few sharper showers are possible
OL,9,Fin the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening with
OL,12,Fa few showery outbreaks of rain. Dry
OL,13,Ffor a time in the early hours before a
OL,14,Frisk of further showers later on.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FMainly cloudy in the morning
OL,17,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,18,FTurning brighter but with a risk of
OL,19,Ffurther showers in the afternoon, some
OL,20,Fpossibly heavy and thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
